e Scheme. The main conditions relating to PMFBY which are binding on States/UTs are as follows:

Adoption of innovative technology especially Smart phones/ hand held devices for capturing conduct of CCEs through CCE-Agri App and use of NCIP platform for flow of information and auto administration of the scheme

State has to conduct requisite number of Crop Cutting Experiments (CCEs) at the level of notified insurance unit area;

CCE based yield data will be uploaded on the National Crop Insurance Portal/submitted to Insurance Company within the notified cut off date ;

State/ UT will make necessary budgetary provision for premium subsidy based on fair estimates, at the beginning of the crop season;

To carry out pilot studies for improved yield estimations using technology.

